title: Box Tops for Education™

creator: General Mills, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Make a difference for schools every time you shop! Download the Box Tops for Education app to start earning today.


~ HOW IT WORKS ~

1. BUY Box Tops products you already know and love.

2. SCAN your receipts in the app.

3. EARN cash for your school!

A check will be sent to your school TWICE a year and the funds can be used towards anything your school needs – whether that’s books, technology, sports equipment, field trips, or anything in between.


~ EARN EVEN MORE ~

Super-charge your earnings with Bonus Offers! No need to pre-select or opt-in before heading to the store. Bonus Offers will be automatically applied for you whenever you purchase eligible products and scan your receipt in the app.

Check out all active Bonus Offers in the app!


~ BELOVED BOX TOPS PRODUCTS ~

Earn on products you know and love: Cheerios®, Lucky Charms®, Cinnamon Toast Crunch®, Nature Valley®, Totino’s®, Old El Paso®, Annie’s®, Yoplait®, Fiber One®, Chex®, Paper Mate®, Lysol® and more!

Download the Box Tops app for a complete list of participating products.


~ ABOUT BOX TOPS ~

Since 1996, Box Tops for Education has helped families earn over $943 million for schools with products they already buy.

Help strengthen schools for generations to come! Download the Box Tops app today, and scan your receipts in the Box Tops mobile app to instantly earn cash for your school.

~ HOW IT WORKS ~

Check out all active Bonus Offers in the app!
